[{"date":"1941-12-06","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c9/d5/241685_HM7Jz.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c9/d5/241685_HM7Jz.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c9/d5/241685_HM7Jz.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c9/d5/241685_HM7Jz.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c9/d5/241685_HM7Jz.jpg"},"summary":"　　又是一年圣诞夜，天空中飘起了鹅毛大雪。所有的人都沉浸在幸福之中，连洞中的小老鼠杰瑞都不例外。他的洞口摆着一个精致的老鼠夹子，上面放置着用红绸缎包扎的奶酪。当然这个警觉的小家伙不会轻易上当，他试探几次之后还是选择放弃。杰瑞来到圣诞树和礼物中间，尽情玩耍，敞开肚子吃喝，偏偏不小心吵醒了正在酣睡的汤姆。在这个节日的夜晚，两个冤家又展开一番激烈的追逐，他们你来我往，互不相让，打破了圣诞夜的温暖与宁静。高潮之处，杰瑞甚至被扔到了屋外…… \r\n　　本片是Tom and Jerry系列第3部作品，并获得1941年奥斯卡金像奖最佳动画短片提名。","name":"The Night before Christmas","name_cn":"圣诞前夜","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1941","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940s","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"米高梅","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Joseph.Barbera","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7(+2)","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"William.Hanna","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short_film","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980年前","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940-1949","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"圣诞前夜"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"メリー・クリスマス"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1941年12月6日"},{"key":"片长","value":"8:19"},{"key":"类型","value":"喜剧 / 动画 / 短片 / 家庭 / 奇幻"},{"key":"导演","value":"Joseph Barbera、William Hanna"},{"key":"IMDb","value":"tt0033952"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":43,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":2,"6":5,"7":16,"8":14,"9":5,"10":1},"score":7.4},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":5,"wish":8,"collect":84,"doing":1},"id":241685,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1941-12-06","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/1f/f0/241686_5j0w0.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/1f/f0/241686_5j0w0.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/1f/f0/241686_5j0w0.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/1f/f0/241686_5j0w0.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/1f/f0/241686_5j0w0.jpg"},"summary":"《快乐旋律》(Merrie Melodies)系列剧场动画短片，曾获得1942年度奥斯卡最佳动画短片奖提名。\r\n\r\n建筑工地上，工头像指挥家一样，指挥工人们像交响乐团一样按照音乐节奏进行工作。背景音乐是常在各种动画片中出现的李斯特《第2号匈牙利狂想曲》。\r\n\r\n本片是导演弗里茨·弗里伦执导的短片中首次出现《第2号匈牙利狂想曲》。弗里伦此后也不止一次地使用过该曲目，例如1946年的《兔子狂想曲》(Rhapsody Rabbit)，1948年的《后巷喧闹剧》(Back Alley Oproar)，以及1949年音乐电影《梦中情》(My Dream Is Yours)的动画部分。","name":"Rhapsody in Rivets","name_cn":"铆钉狂想曲","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1941","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940-1949","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7(+2)","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"其它","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"华纳","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"铆钉狂想曲"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1941年12月6日"},{"key":"片长","value":"7分钟"},{"key":"类型","value":"喜剧 / 动画 / 短片 / 音乐 / 家庭"},{"key":"IMDb","value":"tt0034097"},{"key":"制片人","value":"Leon Schlesinger"},{"key":"导演","value":"Friz Freleng"},{"key":"编剧","value":"Michael Maltese"},{"key":"动画","value":"Gil Turner"},{"key":"音乐","value":"Carl Stalling"},{"key":"动画制作","value":"Leon Schlesinger Productions"},{"key":"发行","value":"Warner Bros. Pictures, The Vitaphone Corporation"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":15,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":2,"6":5,"7":6,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.5},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":2,"wish":2,"collect":32,"doing":0},"id":241686,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1941-12-05","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/b9/c1/359179_8lU6O.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/b9/c1/359179_8lU6O.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/b9/c1/359179_8lU6O.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/b9/c1/359179_8lU6O.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/b9/c1/359179_8lU6O.jpg"},"summary":"Donald is listening to a radio cooking program and mixes up a batch of waffles, but he's distracted and uses rubber cement instead of baking powder. The batter proves to be unusually stiff. First, his spoon gets stuck and the batter acts like a rubber-band airplane, flying the bowl around the room.\r\n\r\nNext, Donald falls with his head in the batter, he tries to get out but initially, he can't (with angry quacking and a lot of bubbles popping), and his tail in the waffle iron. Then he tries to chop it with an ax, and the ax flies up and splits the room in half.\r\n\r\nFinally, he throws the bowl out the door; it sticks to the knob while the bowl gets stuck between two trees. The stretching causes a branch to knock on the door, tricking Donald into opening it and letting the batter back in. After several attempts, he has had enough and rushes to the radio studio where the cooking program is being broadcast, and takes his anger out on Old Mother Mallard.\r\n\r\nAs he approaches the radio station, the radio shakes and wobbles showing that Donald is violently attacking Old Mother Mallard!","name":"Chef Donald","name_cn":"厨师唐老鸭","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1941","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"迪士尼","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Disney","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"唐老鸭","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":1,"tot